{"tid":479684,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺銀魂好似講緊香港","createTime":"2017-11-25T10:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T06:13:46.000Z","uid":134199,"like":14,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c6bf388b7c511095bb0f24aaf740e0b607282671","tid":479684,"uid":134199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"東方之珠<br />\n本來我地既城市有咁既稱譽<br />\n不過都係以前既事<br />\n二十年前突然由大陸黎左班支那人<br />\n佢地既勢力不斷壯大<br />\n令到香港人既勢力衰落<br />\n昔日無邊無際<br />\n有香港人無數夢想馳騁既天空<br />\n而家淨係見到黎自異鄉既蝗蟲<br />\n以往係街上面威風既香港人昂首闊步<br />\n而家淨係見到大模斯樣既支那人<br />\n呢個就係我地既世界<br />\n而且係我地既城市"},{"pid":"8851e8e66896713cd04577c98221a87da57e3a88","tid":479684,"uid":58038,"like":28,"dislike":18,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"巨人又話香港<br />\n銀魂又話香港<br />\n乜撚野都香港 係呀日本咁撚多動漫野留意香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名比人話5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79cd97baf9de4f25c0ca9b38d18dabe3fe12ce5","tid":479684,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巨人又話香港<br />\n銀魂又話香港<br />\n乜撚野都香港 係呀日本咁撚多動漫野留意香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名比人話5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n偷偷地比負皮又唔出聲<br />\n係呀套野有拎過JACKIE CHAN當NETA笑過呀<br />\n但套野開始連載係2003<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2954df4e646b216b0dedab869973dd9ae288d448","tid":479684,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巨人又話香港<br />\n銀魂又話香港<br />\n乜撚野都香港 係呀日本咁撚多動漫野留意香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名比人話5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n偷偷地比負皮又唔出聲<br />\n係呀套野有拎過JACKIE CHAN當NETA笑過呀<br />\n但套野開始連載係2003<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk